  "detailed_description": "Climb It is a platformer and a puzzle game. In Climb It you play as a bouncing ball. Your goal is to advance in a world divided in multiple areas. Each area is inspired by an old arcade game and contains levels to find.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097830/extras/064d08b276d4ace716e71926ac924fc9.poster.avif?t=1666083765\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097830/extras/064d08b276d4ace716e71926ac924fc9.webm?t=1666083765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097830/extras/064d08b276d4ace716e71926ac924fc9.mp4?t=1666083765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Exploration</li></ul>Advance in a 2D world full of obstacles. Be skilful and go from area to area. Find all hidden levels in the world.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Levels</li></ul>Once you are in a level you have to collect all bricks without dying to finish the level. Use your brain and get those bricks by all means !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097830/extras/242968631bfe5350128148eeb1044cf1.poster.avif?t=1666083765\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097830/extras/242968631bfe5350128148eeb1044cf1.webm?t=1666083765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097830/extras/242968631bfe5350128148eeb1044cf1.mp4?t=1666083765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHALLENGE</strong></h2>If you like a challenge this game is made for you. The sadistic level design will complicate things (No refund for broken mouses). But don’t worry, with enough motivation and focus you will succeed !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097830/extras/b2766f00b417d5d8b1e3b62127dd1965.poster.avif?t=1666083765\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097830/extras/b2766f00b417d5d8b1e3b62127dd1965.webm?t=1666083765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097830/extras/b2766f00b417d5d8b1e3b62127dd1965.mp4?t=1666083765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features :</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i>1 Tutorial</i> - A first area to learn the controls and to understand the game mechanics.<br></li><li><i>2 Zones</i> - Each one add it's own touch to the gameplay.<br></li><li><i>60+ Niveaux</i> - Find and finish them.<br></li><li><i>1 Boss</i> - If you go so far...<br></li><li><i>4 à 6 Heures</i> - To finish the game.</li></ul>",
